        <p>What caused <strong>dips or plateaus</strong> in your progress (if you had any)? Was it <strong>time</strong> pressure or time limitations? Did you always struggle with finding a <strong>particular number</strong>? Did you get <strong>bored</strong> with the task and lose focus? Did you reach a plateau and fail to improve beyond this? <strong>Why</strong>?</p>

